---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About Nezzie | Charlotte Wedding Planner &amp; Designer"
  description="Meet Nezzie — the Charlotte-based wedding planner behind Kindred Event Collective. Our story, our philosophy, and the boutique approach that makes planning feel effortless."
  canonical="https://www.kindredeventcollective.com/about.html"
  ogTitle="About Nezzie | Charlotte Wedding Planner"
  ogDescription="The story and philosophy behind Kindred Event Collective, a boutique wedding planning studio in Charlotte, NC."
  active="about"
>
  <main id="main">

    <!-- PAGE HERO -->
    <section class="page-hero" aria-label="About Kindred Event Collective">
      <div class="page-hero__media"></div>
      <div class="page-hero__scrim"></div>
      <div class="container container--narrow">
        <span class="script" style="color:var(--peach);font-size:var(--step-3);">hello, I’m Nezzie</span>
        <h1>The calm behind the celebration</h1>
        <p class="lead">A decade of planning weddings across the Carolinas, and a belief that the best days are the ones you actually get to enjoy.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STORY -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="story-h">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="split">
          <div class="reveal"><div class="ph ph--tall ph--arch" data-label="Founder portrait"></div></div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <span class="eyebrow">My Story</span>
            <h2 id="story-h">It started with a love of bringing people together.</h2>
            <p>I planned my first wedding more than ten years ago and never looked back. What began as a gift for a friend became a calling: building celebrations where every detail feels intentional and every guest feels held.</p>
            <p>Since then, I’ve had the honor of planning over 150 weddings — from intimate vineyard dinners to grand ballroom evenings — always with the same conviction. A wedding is not a checklist. It’s a once-in-a-lifetime story, and it deserves to be told beautifully.</p>
            <p>Today, Kindred Event Collective is a boutique studio by design. I take on a limited number of couples each year so that yours never feels like one of many.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PHILOSOPHY / VALUES -->
    <section class="section section--alt" aria-labelledby="values-h">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head text-center mx-auto reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">What I Believe</span>
          <h2 id="values-h">A planning philosophy</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid--3">
          <article class="card reveal">
            <span class="card__num">&#10043;</span>
            <h3>Stress-free, always</h3>
            <p>My job is to carry the weight so you can stay present. You should feel like a guest at your own wedding.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <span class="card__num">&#10043;</span>
            <h3>Personal, never templated</h3>
            <p>No two couples are alike, so no two weddings should be. Every design starts with your story — not a trend.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <span class="card__num">&#10043;</span>
            <h3>Detail is everything</h3>
            <p>The magic lives in the small things. I obsess over the details so the whole day feels effortless.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LOCAL EXPERTISE -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="local-h">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="split split--reverse">
          <div class="reveal"><div class="ph ph--wide ph--g4" data-label="Charlotte venue"></div></div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <span class="eyebrow">Rooted in the Carolinas</span>
            <h2 id="local-h">Charlotte is home — and our advantage.</h2>
            <p>From The Duke Mansion to Lake Norman estates, mountain venues in Asheville, and hidden garden gems across the Piedmont, I know the Carolinas’ most beautiful spaces and the people who make them shine.</p>
            <p>Those relationships mean trusted vendors, smoother logistics, and doors that open a little more easily — all in service of your day.</p>
            <a class="link-underline mt-md" href="services.html" style="display:inline-block;">See How We Work &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="cta-band" aria-labelledby="cta-h">
      <div class="cta-band__media"></div>
      <div class="cta-band__scrim"></div>
      <div class="container container--narrow">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--peach);">Let’s Meet</span>
        <h2 id="cta-h">I’d love to hear your story.</h2>
        <p>Tell me about the two of you and the day you’re dreaming of. Let’s see if we’re the right fit.</p>
        <a class="btn btn--light" href="contact.html">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
